<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AMINA Académie | Devenez Expert Comptable & CEO</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #4F46E5;
            --primary-hover: #4338CA;
            --accent: #F59E0B;
            --bg-light: #F8FAFC;
            --text-main: #0F172A;
            --text-muted: #475569;
            --white: #FFFFFF;
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-light);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* --- 🧭 PREMIUM NAVBAR --- */
        nav {
            padding: 18px 8%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }
        .logo {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }
        
        /* Desktop Links */
        .nav-links { display: flex; align-items: center; }
        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-right: 25px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--primary); }

        .btn-nav {
            background: var(--text-main);
            color: var(--white) !important;
            padding: 10px 22px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        /* ☰ HAMBURGER ICON (Hidden on Desktop) */
        .menu-btn {
            display: none;
            font-size: 28px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--text-main);
        }

        /* --- 📱 SIDEBAR SLIDE MENU --- */
        .sidebar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            right: -100%; /* Shuru mein screen ke bahar */
            width: 300px;
            height: 100vh;
            background: var(--white);
            z-index: 2000;
            box-shadow: -10px 0 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 25px;
            transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .sidebar.active { right: 0; } /* Jab 'active' class hogi tab slide hoga */
        
        .close-btn {
            align-self: flex-end;
            font-size: 30px;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .sidebar a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
        }
        .sidebar .btn-nav-mobile {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border: none;
        }

        /* Dark Overlay */
        .overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            z-index: 1500;
            display: none;
        }
        .overlay.active { display: block; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav { padding: 15px 5%; }
            .nav-links { display: none; } /* Hide desktop links */
            .menu-btn { display: block; }  /* Show hamburger */
        }

        /* --- HERO SECTION --- */
        .hero {
            padding: 120px 8% 100px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 50px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #EEF2FF 0%, transparent 50%),
                        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, #FFFBEB 0%, transparent 50%);
        }

        .hero-content { flex: 1; max-width: 650px; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: 64px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -2px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .hero h1 span { background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary), #818CF8); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
       
        .hero p { font-size: 20px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 35px; max-width: 550px; }

        .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: center; }

        .btn-main { background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 16px 35px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3); transition: 0.3s; }
        .btn-main:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); }

        .hero-img-box { flex: 1; position: relative; }
        .hero-img { width: 100%; border-radius: 24px; box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); border: 8px solid white; transform: perspective(1000px) rotateY(-5deg); transition: 0.5s; }
        
        .float-badge { position: absolute; bottom: -20px; left: -30px; background: white; padding: 15px 25px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; z-index: 10; }

        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .hero { padding: 80px 5% 60px; flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
            .hero h1 { font-size: 42px; }
            .hero-btns { justify-content: center; }
            .hero-img-box { width: 100%; max-width: 500px; margin-top: 40px; }
            .hero-img { transform: none; }
            .float-badge { left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); bottom: -20px; width: max-content; }
        }

        /* --- BLUEPRINT SECTION --- */
        .blueprint-section { padding: 80px 8%; background: white; text-align: center; }
        .blueprint-section h2 { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .blueprint-section p.sub { color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 18px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 50px; }

        .course-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; text-align: left; }
        .card { background: var(--bg-light); padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0; transition: 0.3s; }
        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: var(--primary); }
        .icon-box { width: 60px; height: 60px; background: white; border-radius: 16px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 25px; box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }

        /* --- TESTIMONIALS --- */
        .testimonials { padding: 100px 8%; background: var(--bg-light); text-align: center; }
        .testi-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 30px; text-align: left; }
        .testi-card { background: white; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid #E2E8F0; transition: 0.3s; }

        /* --- CTA --- */
        .cta-section { padding: 100px 8%; background: var(--text-main); color: white; text-align: center; }
        .cta-section h2 { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .btn-cta { background: var(--accent); color: var(--text-main); padding: 18px 40px; border-radius: 50px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="overlay" id="overlay"></div>

    <nav>
        <a href="/" class="logo">AMINA <span>Académie</span></a>
        
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#programme">Le Programme</a>
            <a href="#temoignages">Témoignages</a>
            <a href="/login">Se connecter</a>
            <a href="/register" class="btn-nav">Rejoindre l'élite</a>
        </div>

        <button class="menu-btn" id="openMenu">☰</button>
    </nav>

    <div class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
        <div class="close-btn" id="closeMenu">✕</div>
        <a href="#programme" class="mobile-link">Le Programme</a>
        <a href="#temoignages" class="mobile-link">Témoignages</a>
        <a href="/login" class="mobile-link">Se connecter</a>
        <a href="/register" class="btn-nav-mobile mobile-link">Rejoindre l'élite ➔</a>
    </div>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div class="badge-pro">🚀 Niveau Pro Max Disponible</div>
            <h1>Devenez un Expert, Bâtissez un <span>Empire.</span></h1>
            <p>Bien plus qu'un cours de comptabilité. Un système complet pour maîtriser la gestion et automatiser vos revenus au Maroc.</p>
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a href="/register" class="btn-main">Accéder au Système</a>
                <a href="#programme" class="btn-sec">Voir le programme ↓</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-img-box">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?q=80&w=1000&auto=format&fit=crop" class="hero-img">
            <div class="float-badge">
                <span>🏆</span>
                <div><h4>100% Pratique</h4><p>Conforme DGI & PCM</p></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="programme" class="blueprint-section">
        <h2>Le Ultimate Blueprint</h2>
        <p class="sub">Notre méthode en 4 piliers pour un succès garanti.</p>
        <div class="course-grid">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">🧠</div>
                <h3>1. Fondation</h3>
                <p>Maîtrisez le Plan Comptable Marocain et la fiscalité (TVA, IS).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">💻</div>
                <h3>2. Logiciels</h3>
                <p>Pratique réelle sur Sage et télédéclarations en direct.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">🤝</div>
                <h3>3. Clients</h3>
                <p>Trouvez des clients B2B et signez des contrats High-Ticket.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <div class="icon-box">⚙️</div>
                <h3>4. Scaling</h3>
                <p>Automatisez vos processus et bâtissez votre propre agence.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="temoignages" class="testimonials">
        <h2>Ils ont bâti leur empire 👑</h2>
        <div class="testi-grid">
            <div class="testi-card">
                <p class="testi-text">"Rentabilisé en 1 mois ! Je gère 5 clients en freelance désormais."</p>
                <div class="testi-user">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?q=80&w=200" class="testi-avatar">
                    <div class="user-info"><h4>Karim B.</h4><p>Freelance</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testi-card">
                <p class="testi-text">"L'interface est magnifique et super motivante. On apprend en pratiquant."</p>
                <div class="testi-user">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108377-be9c29b29330?q=80&w=200" class="testi-avatar">
                    <div class="user-info"><h4>Nadia M.</h4><p>Chef d'Entreprise</p></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Prêt à changer de vie ?</h2>
        <p>Rejoignez AMINA Académie et commencez aujourd'hui.</p>
        <a href="/register" class="btn-cta">Démarrer Maintenant ➔</a>
    </section>

    <script>
        const openBtn = document.getElementById('openMenu');
        const closeBtn = document.getElementById('closeMenu');
        const sidebar = document.getElementById('sidebar');
        const overlay = document.getElementById('overlay');
        const mobileLinks = document.querySelectorAll('.mobile-link');

        // Open Menu
        openBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            sidebar.classList.add('active');
            overlay.classList.add('active');
            document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden'; // Stop scrolling
        });

        // Close Menu Function
        const closeSidebar = () => {
            sidebar.classList.remove('active');
            overlay.classList.remove('active');
            document.body.style.overflow = 'auto'; // Enable scrolling
        };

        closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closeSidebar);
        overlay.addEventListener('click', closeSidebar);
        
        // Auto-close when clicking links
        mobileLinks.forEach(link => {
            link.addEventListener('click', closeSidebar);
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>